metadata.name: Burn Out
metadata.description:
My tributaries, my capillaries 

My hands, my heart petrified

Your disease infested my brain

So, my bones cracked open

Souring my marrow blue

Flushing out my internal red rivers into a sea of midnight Prussian hues

Expelling my spirit into the ether

Burning out my anatomy ashy grey

Leaving my heart empty handed

Soulless and without a care

With nothing
